Mandla Ncikazi, Coach of Lamontville Golden Arrows. DURBAN - News of Mandla Ncikazi's departure from Golden Arrows on Wednesday night sent shock waves in local media. Now speculation is rife as to the destination of the man who took Arrows to their best finish in the league, a club record 4th place. READ: Gavin Lane impressed by KZN teams With Pirates fans calling for changes at the Orlando Stadium-based club, Ncikazi may just be the right tonic to revive the once-dominant Buccaneers.